{"word":"ἀγωνιάω","slug":"ἀγωνιάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀγωνιάω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀγωνία'><el>ἀγωνία</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b>like <el>ἀγωνίζομαι</el>, <i>to contend eagerly, struggle</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to be distressed, be in an agony</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>; <el>περί τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b>; <el>ἐπί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}